Comparable<VCardProperty>
public class Uid
extends UriProperty

A globally unique identifier of the person.

Code sample 

 VCard vcard = new VCard();
 
 Uid uid = new Uid("urn:uuid:b8767877-b4a1-4c70-9acc-505d3819e519");
 vcard.setUid(uid);
 
 //generate a random UID
 uid = Uid.random();
 vcard.setUid(uid);

Property name: UID

Supported versions: 2.1, 3.0, 4.0

Author:
Michael Angstadt
